Package neureka.utility

Class DataConverter.Utility

  • java.lang.Object
    • neureka.utility.DataConverter.Utility
  • Enclosing class:
    DataConverter
    public static class DataConverter.Utility
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a static utility class containing the actual conversion logic which is usually referenced by the Converter lambdas via method signatures... Besides that it also provides the ability to create seeded arrays of data.
